#### [NEW] [workflow-radar.service.ts](file:///C:/Users/owner/.gemini/antigravity/brain/4334d2b3-67f2-4d2e-80b3-6ba8f258d54e/AutoBots1/src/lib/services/workflow-radar.service.ts)
