### 2. Operational Cockpit
#### [NEW] [operator-command-console.ts](file:///C:/Users/owner/.gemini/antigravity/brain/4334d2b3-67f2-4d2e-80b3-6ba8f258d54e/AutoBots1/src/lib/services/operator-command-console.ts)
